          "text": "I love watching it, even during Chinese New Year.",
          "stage": "translated"
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "idx": 4,
      "start": 34.6,
      "end": 37.56,
      "source_text": "所以南非自己過新年都看",
      "by_lang": {
        "zh": {
          "text": "所以南非自己過新年都睇",
          "stage": "refined"
        },
        "en": {
          "text": "So South Africa also celebrates its own New Year.",
          "stage": "translated"
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "idx": 5,
      "start": 37.64,
      "end": 38.76,
      "source_text": "新年才",
      "by_lang": {
        "zh": {
          "text": "新年先至",
          "stage": "refined"
        },
        "en": {
          "text": "It's only just New Year.",
          "stage": "translated"
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "idx": 6,
      "start": 40.0,
      "end": 43.120000000000005,
      "source_text": "這天新10磅仔袁幸瑤出席記者會",
      "by_lang": {
        "zh": {
          "text": "今日新十磅見習騎師袁幸瑤出席記者會",
          "stage": "refined"
        },
        "en": {
          "text": "New 10-pound apprentice jockey Yuen Hang-yiu attended today's press conference.",
          "stage": "translated"
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "idx": 7,
      "start": 43.2,
      "end": 45.2,
      "source_text": "大方分享自己的興趣",
      "by_lang": {
        "zh": {
          "text": "大方分享自己嘅興趣",
          "stage": "refined"
        },
        "en": {
          "text": "Generously sharing their own hobbies.",
          "stage": "translated"
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "idx": 8,
      "start": 45.28,
      "end": 47.0,
      "source_text": "陽光自信的對答",
      "by_lang": {
        "zh": {
          "text": "陽光自信嘅對答",
          "stage": "refined"
        },
        "en": {
          "text": "Confident and sunny responses.",
          "stage": "translated"
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "idx": 9,
      "start": 47.08,
      "end": 50.32,
      "source_text": "加上真摯的笑容, 真的非常圈粉",
      "by_lang": {
        "zh": {
          "text": "加上真摯笑容，真係好攞分",
          "stage": "refined"
        },
        "en": {
          "text": "With a sincere smile, she really gained points.",
          "stage": "translated"
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "idx": 10,
      "start": 50.400000000000006,
      "end": 51.84,
      "source_text": "目前她最大目標",
      "by_lang": {
        "zh": {
          "text": "目前佢最大嘅目標",
          "stage": "refined"
        },
        "en": {
          "text": "Her current biggest goal is...",
          "stage": "translated"
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "idx": 11,
      "start": 51.92,
      "end": 53.44,
      "source_text": "就是盡量吸收經驗",
      "by_lang": {
        "zh": {
          "text": "就係盡量吸收經驗",
          "stage": "refined"
        },
        "en": {
          "text": "Just trying to absorb as much experience as possible.",
          "stage": "translated"
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "idx": 12,
      "start": 53.519999999999996,
      "end": 55.16,
      "source_text": "令自己不斷進步",
      "by_lang": {
        "zh": {
          "text": "令自己不斷進步",
          "stage": "refined"
        },
        "en": {
          "text": "Strive for continuous self-improvement.",
          "stage": "translated"
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "idx": 13,
      "start": 56.04,
      "end": 58.480000000000004,
      "source_text": "強項我覺得是自己的推期",
      "by_lang": {
        "zh": {
          "text": "強項我覺係自己嘅推期",
          "stage": "refined"
        },
        "en": {
          "text": "My strength is my own prediction of the due date.",
          "stage": "translated"
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "idx": 14,
      "start": 58.48,
      "end": 62.08,
      "source_text": "我希望自己比較出色",
      "by_lang": {
        "zh": {
          "text": "希望自己表現更出色",
          "stage": "refined"
        },
        "en": {
          "text": "Hoping to perform even better.",
          "stage": "translated"
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "idx": 15,
      "start": 62.08,
      "end": 65.08,
      "source_text": "若瀚我還在找",
      "by_lang": {
        "zh": {
          "text": "若瀚我仲喺度搵",
          "stage": "refined"
        },
        "en": {
          "text": "If Han, I am still looking for you.",
          "stage": "translated"
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "idx": 16,
      "start": 65.08,
      "end": 68.08,
      "source_text": "應該盡量希望不會有若瀚",
      "by_lang": {
        "zh": {
          "text": "應盡量唔希望會有若瀚",
          "stage": "refined"
        },
        "en": {
          "text": "We hope there will be no further incidents like this.",
          "stage": "translated"
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "idx": 17,
      "start": 68.08,
      "end": 72.08,
      "source_text": "當然全方位地幫自己不停地進步下去",
      "by_lang": {
        "zh": {
          "text": "當然會全方位咁幫自己不停進步落去",
          "stage": "refined"
        },
        "en": {
          "text": "Of course, I will fully dedicate myself to continuous improvement.",
          "stage": "translated"
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "idx": 18,
      "start": 72.08,
      "end": 75.47999999999999,
      "source_text": "始終我也很留意每一位騎師",
      "by_lang": {
        "zh": {
          "text": "始終我都好留意每一位騎師",
          "stage": "refined"
        },
        "en": {
          "text": "I always pay close attention to every jockey.",
          "stage": "translated"
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "idx": 19,
      "start": 75.47999999999999,
      "end": 77.28,
      "source_text": "因為每一位騎師都有他們的特別之處",
      "by_lang": {
        "zh": {
          "text": "因為每一位騎師都有佢哋嘅特別之處",
          "stage": "refined"
        },
        "en": {
          "text": "Because every jockey has their own unique qualities.",
          "stage": "translated"
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "idx": 20,
      "start": 77.28,
      "end": 79.08,
      "source_text": "還有他們的好處",
      "by_lang": {
        "zh": {
          "text": "仲有佢哋嘅好處",
          "stage": "refined"
        },
        "en": {
          "text": "And there are benefits to them as well.",
          "stage": "translated"
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "idx": 21,
      "start": 79.08,
      "end": 80.88,
      "source_text": "而且他們的拆騎方式都不同",
