        "zh": {
          "text": "而且佢哋嘅拆騎方式都唔同",
          "stage": "refined"
        },
        "en": {
          "text": "Moreover, their jockey pairings differ.",
          "stage": "translated"
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "idx": 22,
      "start": 80.88,
      "end": 86.28,
      "source_text": "所以我希望自己可以拿他們每一位騎師的好處",
      "by_lang": {
        "zh": {
          "text": "所以我希望可以取每位騎師嘅好處",
          "stage": "refined"
        },
        "en": {
          "text": "So I hope to draw on each jockey's strengths.",
          "stage": "translated"
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "idx": 23,
      "start": 86.28,
      "end": 89.04,
      "source_text": "放在自己身上就最好",
      "by_lang": {
        "zh": {
          "text": "放喺自己身上就最好",
          "stage": "refined"
        },
        "en": {
          "text": "It is best if it fits oneself.",
